    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines the MPLS Network Action (MNA) Header encoding formats to carry Network Actions and optionally Ancillary Data in the MPLS Label Stack and after the Label Stack. The MPLS Network Action can influence the forwarding decisions or can carry additional OAM information in the MPLS packet. This document follows the MNA requirements specified in draft-ietf-mpls-mna-requirements.</t>
